{"tid":2032310,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港人有抗爭過咩？","createTime":"2020-05-24T04:02:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T04:14:41.000Z","uid":237271,"like":7,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c4a038fad7ee5b8c5e3efbef1c42260b0c09b7ec","tid":2032310,"uid":237271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:02:52.000Z","msg":"中大，理大咁多手足比人拉。咁多手足比人強姦殘殺，義士比人判監當condom。<br />\n社會精英連前途都唔顧罷工迫政府封關，最後香港先抗疫成功。<br />\n連法官都話砍人係高尚情操<br />\n到宜家重係到叫下口號，遊下行，明天繼續返工，奉公守法。最後咩都沒改變。<br />\n咁樣光復到香港？"},{"pid":"a0f1e9bb36c3c2c8e6c4e202ae438de9e4328bd2","tid":2032310,"uid":25473,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:03:42.000Z","msg":"你收收皮啦 係屋企嘆冷氣就抗爭到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f377461fe44723ecb9ff09fe3028396064adb7a2","tid":2032310,"uid":80162,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:04:15.000Z","msg":"笑死呢個時間出啲咁嘅post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c757b3cf3801fcac7526e70892754b71b01b0d4e","tid":2032310,"uid":101307,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:07:24.000Z","msg":"遊行前突然勁多呢類型既po<br />\n<br />\n叫人轉場 (傻既都知想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n送頭 (慣常做法 黎黎去去都係嗰幾隻五毛)<br />\n冇用 (坐係屋企最有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n怨 (冷嘲熱諷 呢種人賤過藍絲 班人肯定唔係手足黎)"},{"pid":"94313ad0cbf08c773d55615902526d2cdbf47b3f","tid":2032310,"uid":254183,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T04:07:34.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n食黃店<br />\n做選民<br />\n成立工會<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63505b5c47610ba68d0e47dcba506df5b315f13b","tid":2032310,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc